---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import CustomButton from "@/components/CustomButton.astro";
import Icons from "@/helpers/Icons.astro";

const wrap = "mx-auto w-full max-w-[77rem] px-4";
---

<Base
  title="Bonus"
  metaTitle="Bonus infissi 2026 | Guida completa Paolucci"
  metaDescription="Guida bonus infissi 2026: Ristrutturazione, Ecobonus, Bonus Sicurezza, requisiti tecnici, documenti e FAQ.">
  <section class="bg-[#eef0f2] py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-24 dark:bg-[#25272a]">
    <div class={wrap}>
      <p class="m-0 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.24em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase sm:text-sm dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
        Bonus infissi 2026
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl leading-[1.05] font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl dark:text-white">
        Tutte le agevolazioni in modo chiaro, divise per bonus.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-lg dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
        Questa pagina riassume in modo operativo i principali incentivi per la
        sostituzione infissi nel 2026, con requisiti, limiti di spesa e documenti
        da gestire.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class={`${wrap} mt-5`}>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-[#f8f9fa] px-4 py-4 sm:px-5 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#303338]">
        <span class="inline-flex h-[1.9rem] w-[1.9rem] items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-[#4e7d1e] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-[#d8f0bc]">
          <Icons icon="CalendarClock" class="h-4 w-4" />
        </span>
        <p class="m-0 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
          <strong class="text-[#262626] dark:text-white">Finestra temporale:</strong>
          {" "}
          2026 indicato come anno ancora favorevole, con progressiva riduzione
          aliquote dal 2027 e ulteriore calo dal 2028 secondo quanto riportato nella fonte.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class={`${wrap} mt-4 grid gap-4`}>
      <article
        id="bonus-ristrutturazione"
        class="rounded-[1.2rem] border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4 shadow-[0_12px_30px_-24px_rgb(0_0_0_/_0.38)] sm:p-5 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#303338]">
        <header class="grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-3">
          <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-[#4e7d1e] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-[#d8f0bc]">
            <Icons icon="House" class="h-5 w-5" />
          </span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="m-0 text-2xl leading-tight font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              Bonus Ristrutturazione
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Intervento classico per sostituzione infissi in abitazioni esistenti.
            </p>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Aliquota
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              50% / 36%
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Prima casa / altre abitazioni
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Massimale
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              96.000 €
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Prima casa (indicazione fonte)
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Recupero
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              10 anni
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              In quote annuali costanti
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="m-0 text-lg leading-tight font-medium text-[#262626] sm:text-xl dark:text-white">
              Cosa rientra
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 grid list-disc gap-1.5 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              <li>Sostituzione serramenti esterni (finestre/portefinestre).</li>
              <li>Intervento finalizzato a migliorare prestazioni e comfort.</li>
              <li>Applicabile su immobili residenziali esistenti.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="m-0 text-lg leading-tight font-medium text-[#262626] sm:text-xl dark:text-white">
              Da verificare
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 grid list-disc gap-1.5 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              <li>Corretto inquadramento dell’intervento con tecnico abilitato.</li>
              <li>Pagamenti tracciabili e documentazione fiscale completa.</li>
              <li>Detrazione ripartita in 10 rate annuali.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article
        id="ecobonus"
        class="rounded-[1.2rem] border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4 shadow-[0_12px_30px_-24px_rgb(0_0_0_/_0.38)] sm:p-5 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#303338]">
        <header class="grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-3">
          <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-[#4e7d1e] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-[#d8f0bc]">
            <Icons icon="Leaf" class="h-5 w-5" />
          </span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="m-0 text-2xl leading-tight font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              Ecobonus
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Dedicato al miglioramento dell’efficienza energetica dell’involucro.
            </p>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Aliquota
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              50% / 36%
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Prima casa / altre abitazioni
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Massimale
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              60.000 €
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Limite indicato dalla fonte
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Recupero
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              10 anni
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Detrazione in quote annuali
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="m-0 text-lg leading-tight font-medium text-[#262626] sm:text-xl dark:text-white">
              Interventi ammessi
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 grid list-disc gap-1.5 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              <li>Finestre e portefinestre comprensive di infissi.</li>
              <li>Persiane, scuri, tapparelle e chiusure oscuranti integrate.</li>
              <li>Porte d’ingresso verso esterno con requisiti energetici idonei.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="m-0 text-lg leading-tight font-medium text-[#262626] sm:text-xl dark:text-white">
              Requisiti tecnici
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 grid list-disc gap-1.5 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              <li>Valori di trasmittanza entro i limiti di zona climatica.</li>
              <li>Asseverazione tecnica quando richiesta.</li>
              <li>Comunicazione ENEA nei casi previsti dalla normativa.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article
        id="bonus-sicurezza"
        class="rounded-[1.2rem] border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4 shadow-[0_12px_30px_-24px_rgb(0_0_0_/_0.38)] sm:p-5 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#303338]">
        <header class="grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-3">
          <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-[#4e7d1e] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-[#d8f0bc]">
            <Icons icon="ShieldCheck" class="h-5 w-5" />
          </span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="m-0 text-2xl leading-tight font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              Bonus Sicurezza
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Focus su protezione antintrusione con serramenti e accessori dedicati.
            </p>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Aliquota
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              50% / 36%
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Prima casa / altre abitazioni
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Obiettivo
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              Protezione
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Ridurre il rischio di effrazione
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white p-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <span class="block text-xs tracking-[0.08em] text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.62)] uppercase dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.7)]">
              Recupero
            </span>
            <strong class="mt-1 block text-2xl leading-none font-bold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
              10 anni
            </strong>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              In quote annuali
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="m-0 text-lg leading-tight font-medium text-[#262626] sm:text-xl dark:text-white">
              Interventi tipici
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 grid list-disc gap-1.5 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              <li>Infissi blindati e vetri antisfondamento.</li>
              <li>Grate, persiane blindate, sistemi anti intrusione integrati.</li>
              <li>Ferramenta di sicurezza e chiusure evolute.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="m-0 text-lg leading-tight font-medium text-[#262626] sm:text-xl dark:text-white">
              Quando conviene
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 grid list-disc gap-1.5 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              <li>Quando il progetto punta su sicurezza + comfort abitativo.</li>
              <li>Quando vuoi integrare design e prestazioni protettive.</li>
              <li>Quando desideri valorizzare l’immobile nel medio-lungo periodo.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class={`${wrap} mt-4`} aria-labelledby="checklist-title">
      <div class="rounded-[1.2rem] border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4 sm:p-5 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#303338]">
        <h2 id="checklist-title" class="m-0 text-2xl leading-tight font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
          Checklist operativa
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
          <article class="m-0 grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-sm font-bold text-[#262626] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-white">1</span>
            <p class="m-0 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Definisci il bonus più adatto con tecnico e consulente fiscale.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="m-0 grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-sm font-bold text-[#262626] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-white">2</span>
            <p class="m-0 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Verifica requisiti energetici e di sicurezza del prodotto scelto.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="m-0 grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-sm font-bold text-[#262626] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-white">3</span>
            <p class="m-0 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Gestisci correttamente pagamenti, fatture e pratiche richieste.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="m-0 grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start gap-2.5">
            <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.2)] text-sm font-bold text-[#262626] dark:bg-[rgb(119_184_45_/_0.35)] dark:text-white">4</span>
            <p class="m-0 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Conserva tutta la documentazione per eventuali controlli successivi.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class={`${wrap} mt-4`} aria-labelledby="faq-title">
      <div class="rounded-[1.2rem] border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4 sm:p-5 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#303338]">
        <h2 id="faq-title" class="m-0 text-2xl leading-tight font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-3xl dark:text-white">
          FAQ
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-2">
          <details open class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white px-3 py-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-lg dark:text-white">
              Posso cambiare solo gli infissi senza rifare tutta la casa?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Sì, in molti casi la sostituzione infissi può accedere agli incentivi anche
              senza una ristrutturazione completa. La scelta del bonus dipende da obiettivi
              (energia/sicurezza) e requisiti tecnici specifici.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white px-3 py-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-lg dark:text-white">
              La detrazione viene recuperata subito?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              No, la detrazione è normalmente ripartita in 10 quote annuali di pari importo.
              Per questo conviene pianificare bene l’investimento e la capienza fiscale.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white px-3 py-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-lg dark:text-white">
              Quali documenti sono essenziali?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              In generale servono fatture, pagamenti tracciabili, documentazione tecnica del
              serramento e, quando previsto, asseverazione e invio ENEA. Il professionista
              incaricato conferma il set documentale corretto per il tuo caso.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.14)] bg-white px-3 py-3 dark:border-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.17)] dark:bg-[#2a2d31]">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold text-[#262626] sm:text-lg dark:text-white">
              Ecobonus e Bonus Sicurezza si possono sempre cumulare?
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(38_38_38_/_0.78)] sm:text-base dark:text-[rgb(255_255_255_/_0.84)]">
              Le regole di cumulabilità dipendono da intervento e inquadramento fiscale.
              Prima di procedere è indispensabile una verifica puntuale con consulente
              tecnico-fiscale.
